## Usage (API)

### Listing Servers 

```pycon
>>> import gripe 
>>> gripe.list()
{"local": [], "foreign": []}
```

### Starting and Stopping Servers 

```pycon
>>> import gripe 

>>> servers = gripe.start(); print(servers)
{ "local": [
    { "pid": 93867, 
      "cwd": "...", 
      "port": 6149 }
  ], 
  "foreign": []
}

>>> gripe.stop(grips=servers['local'])
{"killed": 
  [ { "pid": 93867, 
      "cwd": "...", 
      "port": 6149 } ]
}
```
